---
title: Piccata-Style Sea Bass with Roasted Red Pepper Farro and Broccolini
description: Piccata is an Italian dish that features protein in a savoury sauce of butter, lemon and capers. Flakey sea bass fillets take centre stage in our version and Parmesan cheese boosts up the umami level. We can't forget about the perfect sides: roasted red pepper farro and golden-brown broccolini.
